org.jcvi.jillion.trace.chromat

Interface ChromatogramFileVisitor

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbiChromatogramFileVisitor, ScfChromatogramFileVisitor, ZtrChromatogramFileVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbiChromatogramBuilder.AbiChromatogramBuilderVisitor

    public interface ChromatogramFileVisitor
    ChromatogramFileVisitor is a FileVisitor used for visiting chromatogram files.
    Author:
    dkatzel

      • visitEnd

        void visitEnd()
        The end of the chromatogram has been visited. There will be no more visitXXX methods called for this chromatogram.
